partners.name: Petrol Spy
partners.caption: Cheap petrol finder
partners.description:
**About PetrolSpy**


Fuel app made in Australia for Australia! PetrolSpy is a real-time fuel pricing map for QLD, SA, NSW and WA. You can compare petrol prices submitted by other users near you or by postcode/suburb Australia-wide.

- Real-time fuel pricing map for QLD, SA, NSW and WA 
- Compare petrol prices submitted by other users near you or by postcode/suburb Australia-wide! 
- Chance to win a $25 fuel card every day with every price update 
- FuelCheck prices for NSW


**Other description**


Fuel app made in Australia for Australia! PetrolSpy is a real-time fuel pricing map for QLD, SA, NSW and WA. You can compare petrol prices submitted by other users near you or by postcode/suburb Australia-wide.


**More information**


PetrolSpy has a highly comprehensive coverage of fuel station locations in Australia! Petrol Spy includes site locations for Ampol, Caltex, Woolworths, Shell, Coles Express, BP, 7-Eleven, United Petroleum, Puma and many more independent operators.
